text: Hung Chia-chun (born 28 June 1977) is a Taiwanese taekwondo practitioner. She won a silver medal in lightweight at the 1997 World Taekwondo Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
